heating_controller_config.prompt:
We start with the heating controller. 
If presence sensor exists, the controller mode is "Presence based", 
otherwise "Timetable based"

template_controller_mode_heating_presence_based = {
    "controller_mode": "Presence based",
    "controller_function": "Heating",
    "room_name": {{room_name}},
    "inputs": {
        "airTemperature": {{link_air_temperature}},
        "outsideAirTemperature": {{link_outside_air_temperature}},
        "presence": {{link_presence}}
    },
    "outputs": {
        "airTemperatureSetpoint": {{link_air_temperature_setpoint}},
    }
}

template_controller_mode_heating_timetable_based = {
    "controller_mode": "Timetable based",
    "controller_function": "Heating",
    "room_name": {{room_name}},
    "inputs": {
        "airTemperature": {{link_air_temperature}},
        "outsideAirTemperature": {{link_outside_air_temperature}}
    },
    "outputs": {
        "airTemperatureSetpoint": {{link_air_temperature_setpoint}},
    }
}

Can you give me the configuration file of the heating controller for the room(s) in the JSON data? Please 
only return the configuration file as response.

